        "endTime": 21779,
        "slowStartTime": 28552,
        "slowEndTime": 32893
    },
    {
        "text": "Light pollution is defined as any bad effect as a result of man-made or artificial lights.",
        "startTime": 22768,
        "endTime": 29627,
        "slowStartTime": 34302,
        "slowEndTime": 44666
    },
    {
        "text": "In simple words, this means too much light.",
        "startTime": 29751,
        "endTime": 33433,
        "slowStartTime": 44777,
        "slowEndTime": 50374
    },
    {
        "text": "Several species, including plants, animals and humans are badly affected by light pollution.",
        "startTime": 33701,
        "endTime": 39705,
        "slowStartTime": 50702,
        "slowEndTime": 59782
    },
    {
        "text": "Um... now let's see the components of light pollution.",
